              "file": "bench-artifacts/cache-api.md",
              "patch": "Index: bench-artifacts/cache-api.md\n===================================================================\n--- bench-artifacts/cache-api.md\t\n+++ bench-artifacts/cache-api.md\t\n@@ -0,0 +1,44 @@\n+# Cache API\n+\n+An in-memory cache implementation using `Map` for storing key-value pairs.\n+\n+## `createCache()`\n+\n+Creates a new cache instance with get, set, delete, and clear methods.\n+\n+```js\n+import { createCache } from './cache'\n+\n+const cache = createCache()\n+```\n+\n+## Methods\n+\n+### `get(key)`\n+\n+Retrieves a value stored in the cache by key.\n+\n+- **Parameter:** `key` (any) - The cache key to look up\n+- **Return:** The value associated with the key, or undefined if not found\n+\n+### `set(key, value)`\n+\n+Stores a value in the cache using the specified key.\n+\n+- **Parameters:**\n+  - `key` (any) - The cache key\n+  - `value` (any) - The value to store\n+- **Return:** The stored value\n+\n+### `delete(key)`\n+\n+Removes a value from the cache by key.\n+\n+- **Parameter:** `key` (any) - The cache key to delete\n+- **Return:** true if the key existed and was deleted, false otherwise\n+\n+### `clear()`\n+\n+Removes all entries from the cache.\n+\n+- **Return:** undefined\n",
              "additions": 44,
              "deletions": 0,
              "status": "added"
            }
          ]
